Products.RichDescription:
Macro Hemp Corn Chips Jalapeno contain omega 3 from hemp seeds.

What's inside matters.

Give in to these tempting corn chips & enjoy a treat that's 'nacho' regular snack! Made with linseeds & hemp seeds, these corn chips are full of goodness with none of the baddies.

Did you know that hemp is possibly one of the world's most nutritious plants, providing you with plant-based omega 3.

A recommended serve is 16 chips.. but who's counting anyway.

- Suitable for Vegetarians.

- No artificial colours, flavours or preservatives.

You care about what goes into your food and we do too. That's why we do our best to source simple ingredients and bring you food you can trust, made with spoonfuls of love, care and dedication. It's good food for a better you.

Gluten free.

Packed with flavour.

Nothing artificial.

Mild.

Products.RichDescription:
Macro Hemp Corn Chips Kale & Wasabi contain omega 3 from hemp seeds.

What's inside matters.

We've combined the traditional crunch of a corn chip & given it a slight Japanese flavour twist, then added the goodness of kale & a touch of hemp for yummy goodness that'll make you go, "kale yeah!".

Did you know that hemp is possibly one of the world's most nutritious plants, providing you with plant-based omega 3.

A recommended serve is 16 chips... but who's counting anyway?

- Suitable for vegetarians.

- No artificial colours, flavours or preservatives.

You care about what goes into your food and we do too. That's why we do our best to source simple ingredients and bring you food you can trust, made with spoonfuls of love, care and dedication. It's good food for a better you.

Gluten free.

Source of fibre.

Packed with flavour.

Nothing artificial.
